<P>
   TECHNOLOGY
</P>
<P>
   COXNET PTECH _ (EDS: This is the CoxNet PTECH page for the
current week. This layout is available Tuesday after 2 p.m. EST.)
</P>
<P>
   COXNET PTECH 0208 -- Electronic tax filing may prove to be a
