</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Bad jokes, good Web site
 &HT;    By Staff Reports
 &HT;    c. 2000 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   ATLANTA _ Question: Where's the one place you shouldn't take a
dog shopping? Answer: A flea market. If you liked that
knee-slapper, take a look at the Kratts' Creatures Web site, at
www.pbs.org/kratts. You can enjoy a joke and explore the creature
world, creature clubhouse and the creature of the week.
</P>
<P>
   SNOW FIGHT
</P>
<P>
   The kids are on a mission in Nickelodeon's newest flick ``Snow
Day,'' which starts Feb. 11. They're fighting to stay out of school
for that elusive Second Snow Day. But the Snowplowman is always out
to thwart their efforts! Will they be able to stop him? Will you
like the movie? Write us at nfk(at)ajc.com and tell us what you
think. Also check out the movie's Web site at snowdaymovie.nick.com
to send snowball messages to your friends!
</P>
