</P>
<P>
   3. What are the common names for: caries, myopia, missing
patellar reflex?
</P>
<P>
   4. George Washington appointed the first secretary of state,
chief justice, secretary of war, attorney general, and postmaster
general. Name them.
</P>
<P>
   Answers: 1. Majorca, Minorca, and Ibiza 2. Violetta 3. Cavities,
