   ONLINE-INVESTING (Undated) _ In the latest frontier for online
investing, your can buy individual stocks directly on the Internet
from companies like Home Depot, or use an e-broker that specializes
in fractional shares. By Dolores Kong. 700 words.
</P>
<P>
   MONEY-TRAUSCH (Undated) _ The money buzz could drive a person to
Vegas. It starts with the words, ``I know a guy who ... '' and
explodes into yet another tale of riches. By Susan Trausch.
</P>
<P>
   FINANCE-HOOKER (Undated) _ Projecting investors' financial goals
is almost impossible because of uncertain savings and portfolio
growth. By Kenneth Hooker.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; The Boston Globe &LR;  &QC;
