<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-HEALTH-WEB-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Clinical tests offer alternatives
 &HT;    By M.A.J. McKenna
 &HT;    c. 2000 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
