<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-02-07 17:05 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9391 &Cx1f; sci-z
u a BC-SCI-WATCH-NYT &LR;      02-07 0686
