<P>
   SCHOOL-DISSECT (Boston) _ It's as unforgettable as the prom: A
frog stretched out on a table, frozen in chemical preservatives,
awaiting dissection. But a Massachusetts bill would allow
alternative methods -- including computer-generated specimens. By
Sandy Coleman. 1200 words. Photo
