<SLUG> BC-BIZMAGS08-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;    
 &HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Don't let the good times go to your head
 &HT;    By Tom Walker
 &HT;    c. 2000 Cox News Service
