<P>
   w/FEAR08 _ A string of horizontal stabilizer problems on MD-80
series jetliners _ including one that forced an Alaska Airlines jet
to return Saturday night shortly after takeoff _ has some
passengers scared about flying the model. Are passengers
cancelling, switching to flights featuring other planes?
</P>
