</P>
<P>
   CHRISTIES-FEES (New York) _ Faced with class-action lawsuits and
a 3-year-old antitrust investigation into possible collusion
between Sotheby's and Christie's, the world's two largest auction
houses, Christie's announced Monday that it was changing the fees
it charges buyers and sellers. By Carol Vogel.
</P>
<P>
   (Will move by 9 p.m. ET.)
</P>
<P>
