<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-02-07 21:43 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9760 &Cx1f; taf-z
s t BC-PRACTICAL-TRAVELER-2T     02-07 1091
